DMW boss, David ‘Davido’ Adeleke has hinted on plans to build his “dream” home in Banana Island. Davido shared this via Twitter on Thursday while showing off the land gifted to him in March by his father, Adedeji Adeleke. He attached a tweet which reads: “Let’s build our dream home.”   Rick Ross arrives Lagos 10 years after for Easter concert     Marriage not ticket to financial freedom – Didi Ekanem     Nigerian artistes very similar to politicians –…   He had disclosed developing the land to something special for his children while announcing the gift to his fans. The ‘Fem’ crooner hosted a large gathering in January at his house warming ceremony for his second home in Banana Island, Lagos.